ed="T" n="0882a07"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0882a07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>越州開元寺<persName key="A012266">曇休</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0882a08"/><persName key="A012266">釋曇休</persName>，字<persName key="A012266">德敷</persName>，姓李氏。器度宏廓，志行修勅。<lb
ed="T" n="0882a09"/>納法已來，未容少缺。習通漸教，頗至精微。<lb
ed="T" n="0882a10"/>四分律、相部、疏宗，蔚成淵府。初機請學，皆到<lb
ed="T" n="0882a11"/>甚深。<persName key="A012266">休</persName>於講訓之餘，紏繩寺任。伊寺者，<anchor xml:id="beg0882001"/>梁<anchor xml:id="end0882001"/><lb
ed="T" n="0882a12"/>所創，年涉四百，雖觀閣巋然，且<anchor xml:id="beg0882002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>㯫</sic><corr>櫨</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0882002"/>梲傾<lb
ed="T" n="0882a13"/>弛。<persName key="A012266">休</persName>革故有方，締構無隙，特加壯麗，輪焉<lb
ed="T" n="0882a14"/>奐焉。又護國經樓迨諸棟宇，悉見鼎新，次以<lb
ed="T" n="0882a15"/>寺之門樓也，則<date key="j19782341978588" notAfter-iso="+0705-02-02" notBefore-iso="+0704-02-14">長安四年</date>故<persName key="A004177">曇一律師</persName>之經<lb
ed="T" n="0882a16"/>始也，既而頹廢，仍重整覆，一同創制。復慊<lb
ed="T" n="0882a17"/><date key="j19585081960698" notAfter-iso="+0656-02-09" notBefore-iso="+0650-02-10">永徽中</date><persName key="A001046">康僧會法師</persName>應身堂座卑庳，乃<anchor xml:id="beg0882003"/>募<anchor xml:id="end0882003"/>人<lb
ed="T" n="0882a18"/>釐變舊規，<date key="j20355242040147" notAfter-iso="+0873-08-18" notBefore-iso="+0860-12-21"><name>咸通</name>年中</date>也。<persName key="A012266">休</persName>之一言，檀信響應。<lb
ed="T" n="0882a19"/>後終于<placeName key="PL000000013226">住寺</placeName>，今之<placeName key="PL000000013226">大善伽藍</placeName>是也。</p>
